rails plugin
  loader
    sets test mode
    loads rails application
    compiles assets??
  worker
    loads application envionment
    destroys old databases
    creates new databases

rspec plugin
  loads spec/spec_helper unless RSpec is defined
  executes a test loading strategy (test examples vs test files)
  is presented with the test to run, returns true if the test should be run
  takes care of its own formatter

minitest plugin
  loads minitest environment

testunit plugin

cucumber plugin

sinatra plugin


